snippet.textDisplay:
First comment! 😁

What an amazing piece of music! I was already on board from the very first second but the very moment Arnob's part began, it ascended me to a different plane of existence.

I cannot be more grateful to Coke Studio for this platform for bringing our cultural songs into the modern era for generations to come. It has also introduced me to so many talented and wonderful musician and artists I was not familiar with, take the lovely Sunidhi herself! She's incredible! The fact that she and Arnob are a couple makes this video even more magical! 

And to Arnob, I can't be thankful enough. His music has been a huge part of my teenage and adolescent life. You are truly one of the greatest of your generation and, perhaps, even beyond.

Finally, I gotta give credit to Adit Rahman for the incredible composition. Before now Darale Duare was my most favourite song but this my top that as my most favourite now. The song just radiates pure joy!
